@node TECH "Technical Support"

@{FG Highlight}Before you call for help:@{FG Text}

1. Check the @{"Troubleshooting" link PageStream3:Help/PGS.tro/MAIN} section first to see if your question is
already answered.

2. Know the version of PageStream installed. (Check the Navigator.)

3. Know your registration number. (Choose Project/About.)

4. Know which Amiga model you have, and which version of the operating
system is installed.

If you received a bad disk, call @{"sales" link FONE} for a replacement disk. We will
replace bad disks within 90 days of purchase.



@{FG Highlight}90 Days Free Support@{FG Text}

Your purchase of PageStream3 includes 90 days of free technical support
by phone from the date of your first phone call. This is designed to help
you install your program and to resolve any problems you have while
getting started.

Call 314-256-9333 to use your 90 days of free support. Note: you cannot
call the toll-free number for free support. That number is reserved for
priority access for customers paying for technical support.

You MUST be registered to use your free 90 days of technical support. If
you have not sent in your registration card, you must do so before
calling for help.


@{FG Highlight}Free Mail Support@{FG Text}

Mail or fax your questions to us and we will mail you answers. (Our
technical support department will not fax replies unless you have
purchased the Paid Annual Support pport plan.)
@{code}
Soft-Logik Publishing Corporation
Attn: Technical Support
315 Consort Drive
St. Louis, MO  63011  USA

Fax: 314-256-7773
@{body}
@{body}
Include the information requested in the `Before you call' section above.


@{FG Highlight}Free Online Support@{FG Text}

Using a modem for technical support is a cost-effective means of getting
your questions answered. You can post a question and receive a reply
within a day or even a few hours. Patches to the latest version of
PageStream3 are made available online for you to download.

We recommend the GEnie network for technical support. Soft-Logik
technical support representatives answer questions on GEnie each business
day.

If you are not a GEnie user and you live in the USA or Canada, here is
how to join:

1. Set your communications software for half duplex (local echo) at 2400
baud (9600 baud access is available after you signup).

2. Dial toll free: 1-800-638-8369 in the United States or Canada.

3. Enter JOINGENIE at the prompt and then press Return.

4. When asked for your special offer code, enter PAJ528 and then press
Return.

5. Have a major credit card ready. In the United States, you may also use
your checking account number. (There is a $2.00 monthly fee for all
checking accounts.) In Canada, VISA and MasterCard only.

For more information, call 1-800-638-9636 from 9am to midnight Eastern
time, Monday to Friday, and from noon to 8pm on Saturday or Sunday.

Once you have logged on to GEnie as a validated member and are at the top
prompt, type SOFTLOGIK (or move 385).

On CompuServe, type GO AMIGAVEN for support. On Internet, post a message
in comp.sys.amiga.applications or email tech@slpc.com. (Patches are
available on Aminet in biz\patch.) On Portal, support is provided by
non-Soft-Logik employees; type GO SOFTLOGIK.


@{FG Highlight}Paid Annual Support@{FG Text}

If you are a desktop publishing professional, you know how frustrating it
can be to need an answer and not have anyone to turn to. With the
Soft-Logik Annual Support plan, help will only be a toll-free phone call
away. For a low annual charge, Soft-Logik Annual Support provides
unlimited toll-free support for one user. It's like having your own
consulting service on hand!
 
Call 1-800-829-5816 toll-free for Paid Annual Support, 314-256-9333 if
you live outside the United States or Canada.

If all our representatives are busy, we'll call you back!

Fax us your questions, we'll fax you answers---fax 314-256-7773.

An additional 25% discount off the price of new Soft-Logik releases.

An additional 25% discount off the price of major updates.

Free minor updates (3.0g, 3.0h...) sent automatically.

$149 per year for each Soft-Logik application.


@{FG Highlight}Paid Per Call Support@{FG Text}

Not everybody needs the benefits of the Annual Support plan, so it may be
more cost-effective for you to pay for 15 minutes of technical support at
a time. If your question is short, you can ask additional questions up to
the 15 minute per call maximum. If your problem takes longer than 15
minutes to solve, or if it requires follow-up calls, you'll still only be
charged a single flat fee.
 
Call 1-800-829-5816 toll-free for Paid Per Call Support, 314-256-9333 if
you live outside the United States or Canada.

$25 per problem resolution; 15 minute maximum for multiple questions.

VISA, MasterCard, Discover or American Express card required.
