@{FG Highlight}Trademarks@{FG Text}

PageStream, TypeSmith, Art Expression, PageLiner, BME and Soft-Logik are
trademarks or registered trademarks of Soft-Logik Publishing Corporation.
Amiga, AmigaDOS and Workbench are registered trademarks of
Commodore-Amiga, Inc. Macintosh is a trademark of Apple Computer Inc.
MS-DOS and Windows are trademarks or registered trademarks of MicroSoft
Corporation. IBM is a trademark of International Business Machines
Corporation. Professional Draw, Professional Page and PageSetter are
trademarks or registered trademarks of Gold Disk, Inc. Adobe,
Illustrator, and PostScript are trademarks of registered trademarks of
Adobe Systems Inc.

All other trademarked names used herein are used for the purposes of
identification and for the benefit of the trademark holder. No
infringement of trademarks is intended. Trademarks remain the property of
the trademark holder.

@{FG Highlight}Software License@{FG Text}

The purchaser of this product is licensed to duplicate and/or store the
software program for the use of the purchaser on one computer at one
time. The unauthorized duplication and/or storage of this product in any
storage medium is illegal and is prohibited by federal and international
laws. Reproduction of PageStream for the use of others or for
installation on more than one computer constitutes software piracy, a
criminal offense.

Contact the Sales department for information on site licenses and dealer
copies.

@{FG Highlight}Transfer of Software License@{FG Text}

There is only one software license and registration number per copy of
PageStream. Upgrades to the program are considered the same program for
legal purposes. If you sell your copy of PageStream you are selling the
software license and registration number. You cannot sell your previous
version of PageStream and keep the latest version because there is only
one software license.

@{FG Highlight}Upgrading@{FG Text}

Soft-Logik regularly upgrades PageStream. By immediately returning your
registration card you will enable Soft-Logik to keep you aware of the
latest releases. Soft-Logik reserves the right to charge a processing fee
for maintenance upgrades and an upgrade fee for major upgrades.

@{FG Highlight}Warranty@{FG Text}

Soft-Logik Publishing Corporation makes no warranties, either express or
implied, regarding the enclosed computer software package, its
merchantability or its fitness for any particular purpose. The exclusion
of implied warranties is not permitted by some states or countries so the
above exclusion may not apply to you. This warranty provides you with
specific legal rights. There may be other rights that you have which vary
among states and countries.

Soft-Logik Publishing Corporation warrants the magnetic media to be free
from physical defects for 90 days after purchase. Soft-Logik will replace
the disks free of charge should they fail within this time. Every effort
has been made to ensure the accuracy of this manual. Because PageStream
is constantly being improved, Soft-Logik cannot guarantee its accuracy
after publication and disclaims liability for changes, errors and
omissions, or damages resulting therefrom.

